             was again indicted for <rs id="t17900915-118-off612" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900915-118-off612" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900915-118-off612" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               obtaining by false pretences twenty-four half pint tumblers, and twelve adelphi wine glasses
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900915-118-victim1155" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Pearman
                  <interp inst="t17900915-118-victim1155" type="surname" value="Pearman"></interp>
