                     <interp inst="t17900915-118-person1157" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am clerk to Mr. Spode.</p>
               <p>(The note shewn him.)</p>
               <p>This is not my hand writing.</p>
